  <para>
    <classname>JacobiPreconditioner</classname> is a <xref
    linkend="RegisteredClass-Preconditioner"/> that simply inverts the
    diagonal part of the matrix.  It's quick and easy to compute, but
    usually not as effective as the other non-trivial preconditioners.
  </para>
  <para>
    <classname>JacobiPreconditioner</classname> uses the
    <classname>DiagPreconditioner</classname> from <ulink
    url="http://math.nist.gov/sparselib++/">SparseLink++</ulink>.
  </para>



